2.00	HRSG	Heat recovery steam generator	A heat recovery steam generator or HRSG is an energy recovery heat exchanger that recovers heat from a hot gas stream. It produces steam that can be used in a process or used to drive a steam turbine.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bf/ModularHRSG-Picture.JPG/220px-ModularHRSG-Picture.JPG
